==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crispy
<hw>Crisp"y</hw> <pr>(-?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Formed
into short, close ringlets; frizzed; crisp; <as>as, <ex>crispy</ex>
locks</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Crisp; brittle; <as>as, a <ex>crispy</ex> pie
crust</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crissal</ent>⟦br⟧
